# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Fagom Professional Template — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this file and rename it to ".env"  (remove the ".example" part)
#   2. Set your desired admin password below
#   3. Run "npm run build" — the password is compiled into the bundle
#
# IMPORTANT:
#   - Never share your .env file or commit it to version control
#   - If you change the password, run "npm run build" again and re-upload
#     the "dist" folder to your hosting
#   - If you leave VITE_ADMIN_PASSWORD empty, the admin panel
#     will be accessible without a password (useful during development)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Admin panel password — choose something strong and memorable
VITE_ADMIN_PASSWORD=your-strong-password-here
